There is something called TPS (Telephone Preference Service) in this country: if you register with them, no cold-callers can ring you - & companies can actually be fined for breaching this. (There are a few exceptions though, such as research surveys - which are excluded from TPS blocking on the grounds that it would 'skew the results' of their demographic sample...). But definitely worth doing though.



